'''''Napoleon at Waterloo''''' is a 1984 [[computer wargame]] published by Krentek Software.

==Gameplay==
''Napoleon at Waterloo'' is a game in which the player controls Napoleon while the computer commands the forces of [[Arthur Wellesley, 1st Duke of Wellington|Wellington]] at the [[Battle of Waterloo]].<ref name="CGW22"/>

==Reception==
